SUMMARY:The Unauthorized Rolling Stones at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Deep in the redwoods\, we’re turning up the grit\, swagger\, and sound of one of the greatest rock bands of all time… \nJoin us this March for an Unauthorized Rolling Stones Tribute Night — a raw\, high-energy performance channeling the spirit of Mick\, Keith\, and the Stones’ iconic catalog. Expect all the classics\, a little attitude\, and a whole lot of rock ’n roll under the trees. \nFeaturing Rudy Colombini\, a North Bay music legend known for his powerhouse vocals and magnetic stage presence\, bringing decades of rock ’n roll experience to this unforgettable night. \nBrown Sugar • Gimme Shelter • Start Me Up • and more \nAll Ages
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-unauthorized-rolling-stones-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Unauthorized-Rolling-Stones-1S.jpg
