SUMMARY:Comedy Night at Cloverdale Performing Arts Center Featuring Joe Klocek
DESCRIPTION:Joe currently runs two monthly shows in San Francisco. At Cobbs Comedy Club\, his game show\, “Get It!?” Is becoming the next big thing. At The Punch Line\, Joe Klocek & Friends\, is his chance to show off new talent to audiences and headline for an hour. \nJoe also has a podcast about stand-up comedy\, current events and anything interesting. It is on YouTube and it’s called The Splain. \nJoe had a two month “comic in residency” at the first comedy club in Shanghai\, China. \nJoe has been featured on NPR’s\, “Snap Judgement” and has also appeared on Comedy Centrals\, “Live at Gotham” NBC’s\, “Last Comic Standing” and was commentator for the Emmy award wining documentary\, “A Bridge so Far” \nJoe has also been a runner-up in the “San Francisco International Comedy Competition” and the “Seattle Comedy Competition.”
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/comedy-night-at-cloverdale-performing-arts-center-featuring-joe-klocek/
LOCATION:Cloverdale Performing Arts Center\, 209 N. Cloverdale Blvd.\, Cloverdale\, CA
CATEGORIES:Comedy
GEO:38.8066;-123.018
