SUMMARY:Tom Rigney & Flambeau - plus Kevin Russell and Friends
DESCRIPTION:A fun survey of Americana Music disguised as a dance party! Come listen and dance to cajun\, rock\, blues\, pop and country music by these stars of the Sonoma county music scene.\nTom Rigney’s band of all stars simmers and cooks with musical intelligence.Their high energy live show features tight ensemble playing\, deeply infectious grooves\, and rich soloing. Renowned guitarist Danny Caron (Marcia Ball\, Clifton Chenier\, Charles Brown)\, boogie queen Caroline Dahl\, Steve Parks on bass and Brent Rapone on drums have carved evocative and powerfully uplifting music\, led by that guy in the red boots. \nThe Occasionals\nAmericana\, pop and rock music dipped in country and the blues. Linda Ronstadt and John Prine get into a car with Willie Dixon and Big Mama Thornton\, crank up the radio & rock it all the way home! Fantastic originals and lively covers by Hank Williams\, BB King\, Chuck Berry\, James Taylor\, Carole King and more! \nfeaturing\nLoralee Christensen – powerhouse vocals & infectious playful energy\nPaul Olguin – bass & questionable sense of humor\nDallis Craft – piano & pop star vocals\nBrent Rapone – drums and impeccable rhythm\nCandy Girard – fiddle\, vocals & killer smile\nKevin Russell – guitar & vocals & set list maker \nTICKETS: \nPURCHASE IN ADVANCE AND SAVE!\nZones A & B ensure a seat. Zone C has limited seating\, plus standing room. \nZone A  $30\nZone B $25\nZone C $20 (does not guarantee seating)\nTickets at the door $30 (Zone C only) \nDoors open 6:00pm.  \nOur kitchen serves our All New Menu from the time doors open until end of intermission. (Kitchen available only at events with 60 or more advance tickets sold)
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/tom-rigney-flambeau-plus-kevin-russell-and-friends/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Tom-Rigney.jpg
GEO:38.44252;-122.71621
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=The California Theatre of Santa Rosa 528 7th Street Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=528 7th Street:geo:-122.71621,38.44252
END:VEVENT
