SUMMARY:Nate Lopez at Lagunitas
DESCRIPTION:Nate Lopez delivers a sound that is much more than a typical solo artist: With the ability to play bass and guitar at the same time on one instrument\, Nate creates music that captivates audiences\, from dynamic original music to solo cover arrangements of timeless favorites from many styles\, including Jazz\, Blues\, Pop\, Rock\, and Funk.\n\nMusic is at its heart interactive.\nNate doesn’t play at the audience\, he plays with them\, providing a deep and unique groove for each show that compels listeners to tap their feet\, bob their heads\, dance\, and really feel each song.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/nate-lopez-at-lagunitas-5/
